= 0 C.E. --- Grand Bazaar #emph[(Special)] <grand-bazaar-special>
#link("#")[← Buildings & Wonders]

== Purpose <purpose>

Trade was the lifeblood of many ancient cities. Market districts often grew into vast commercial centers where merchants negotiated deals, organized caravans, and coordinated trade with nearby settlements.

The Grand Bazaar centralizes commercial activity, improving the efficiency of your merchants and strengthening the reach of your markets.

Once built, the Grand Bazaar:

increases the trading ratio with farming villages

expands the capacity of your Marketplace by 50%

This allows merchants to move greater quantities of goods and secure more favorable trade deals.

~ Strategic focus: #strong[Commerce] / #strong[diplomacy]
